  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nUse the gossipsub subscription and unsubscription events to keep track of which peers are subscribed to which topic. \r\n\r\nThen build a HTTP API endpoint that collects number of peers per topic and include it as a metric in grafana. This will be nice to visually understand how connected we are to the attestation subnets at any given point in time. \r\n\r\nIt will also make it easier for us to diagnose issues with discovering and connecting to peers on subnets and verify our attestation inclusion rate into blocks. \r\n",
